{"id":7138,"date":"2024-01-27T11:37:56","date_gmt":"2020-03-27T06:07:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=7138"},"modified":"2024-11-18T13:43:29","modified_gmt":"2024-11-18T08:13:29","slug":"living-room-corner-decor","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-corner-decor\/","title":{"rendered":"Fill Those Awkward Spaces! Corner Decoration Ideas For Your Living Room"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Carefully decorated corners can transform awkward, empty corners into eye-catching zones.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to home decor every inch of space needs to be embellished for a complete look. These tiny spaces in your living room can be filled with furniture, pieces of artwork, shelves and can make all the difference in those corners of your living room. Keep reading for some new and stylish corner decorating ideas to glam up your living room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Love That Corner Table For Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Show some love for those corners with a corner table. It\u2019s small, handy, and often not given as much importance as other pieces of furniture. A corner table adds a finishing touch to your&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/living-room-design\/\">living room\u2019s interior design<\/a>. Rest your coffee or a book on a nicely designed corner table \u2013 square, round or geometric, anything works! You can also try nesting tables (two or more tables that fit in together), an excellent option for a space-challenged home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"attachment_7140\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014028\/corner-table-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Corner table for living room give a whole new look to living room\" class=\"wp-image-7140\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014028\/corner-table-for-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014028\/corner-table-for-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014028\/corner-table-for-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014028\/corner-table-for-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Spice up your corner with an accent table to give a whole new look to the living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Turn corner spaces into the center of attention\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/18105546\/turn-corner-spaces-into-center-of-attention.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Shelves, Storage And Style For Corner Decoration<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Did you think corner shelves are outdated? Think again! For those who live in small apartments, large pieces of furniture aren\u2019t feasible, especially if they lack functionality. Corner shelves are a great way to create extra space. Free standing shelves give you extra storage and bring in some character to a room. They are easy to place, can be moved around and fit in really well in those nooks. This apart from sprucing up the decor quotient of your living room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"attachment_7141\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014033\/corner-shelf-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Corner shelf for living room give you extra storage and bring in some character to a room\" class=\"wp-image-7141\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014033\/corner-shelf-for-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014033\/corner-shelf-for-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014033\/corner-shelf-for-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014033\/corner-shelf-for-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A free standing shelf is easy to place and offers good storage space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-showcase-designs\/\">Modern Showcase Designs For Your Living Room<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Fill A Corner With A Bookshelf For Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A bookshelf by far is one of easiest and smartest ways to fill corner spaces. And don\u2019t we all love a reading corner with our favourite authors? You do right? See this bookshelf that stands tall from floor to ceiling? It\u2019s filled with books \u2013 not only does it give you all that space to store your bestsellers, but also brings in beautiful colours to this space! You can decorate your bookshelf with some antique items and decor items as well for a good mix of elements.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"attachment_7142\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014036\/living-room-corner-decor-with-bookshelf.jpg\" alt=\"Living room corner decor with a bookshelf will add value to corners of living room\" class=\"wp-image-7142\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014036\/living-room-corner-decor-with-bookshelf.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014036\/living-room-corner-decor-with-bookshelf-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014036\/living-room-corner-decor-with-bookshelf-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014036\/living-room-corner-decor-with-bookshelf-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A bookshelf will add value to the corners of your living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also Read <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/bookshelf-design-for-home\/\">Bookshelf Design Ideas For Your Home\u00a0<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Floating Shelves To The Rescue<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking to create more space? Well, have you ever thought about using floating shelves in those empty corners of your living room? They have excellent potential to turn awkward spaces into a beautiful nook and give you a bit of extra storage too. Floating shelves provide a functional and stylish design to the forgotten corners of living rooms as we see in this image. Whether you\u2019re looking to display your collection of memorabilia or creating a bookshelf, floating shelves will do the job just fine!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"attachment_7143\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014040\/living-room-corner-ideas-floating-shelves.jpg\" alt=\"Living room corner decor ideas to turn awkward spaces into a beautiful nook and give extra storage\" class=\"wp-image-7143\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014040\/living-room-corner-ideas-floating-shelves.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014040\/living-room-corner-ideas-floating-shelves-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014040\/living-room-corner-ideas-floating-shelves-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014040\/living-room-corner-ideas-floating-shelves-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Take advantage of protruding corners with floating shelves<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Indoor Plants For A Natural Ambiance<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Indoor plants make for beautiful decor. A dash of green in any space automatically lifts the energy and vibe of a room. Plants are great additions to corner spaces too. Be it a leafy one or a flowering pot, they are always noticed by your guests. If you want to maximise the potential of your living room, then place a large-leaf plant in a solid coloured pot. Place it on the floor or on a stand, either way greenery is a fail safe way to fill empty corners.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"attachment_7144\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014045\/living-room-corner-decor-with-indoor-plants.jpg\" alt=\"Living room corner decor with indoor plants for a natural ambiance\" class=\"wp-image-7144\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014045\/living-room-corner-decor-with-indoor-plants.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014045\/living-room-corner-decor-with-indoor-plants-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014045\/living-room-corner-decor-with-indoor-plants-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014045\/living-room-corner-decor-with-indoor-plants-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">People with a green thumb appreciate the charm of indoor plants<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Include Extra Furniture<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Occasional furniture is great for empty corners. A single sofa chair or a side table brings in that extra oomph to your living room. More seating in the corners of your living room makes this space feel cozy. Create a special place where you can curl up with your favorite author or a steaming cup of hot tea. And if your living room is really large you can use all four corners with a variety of seating options to make it the major design element of the room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\" id=\"attachment_7145\"><a href=\"https:\/\/pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/bookmarklet\/?is_video=false&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designcafe.com%2Fblog%2Fliving-room-interiors%2Fliving-room-corner-decor%2F&amp;media=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.designcafe.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F21014048%2Fliving-room-corner-furniture.jpg&amp;description=Living%20room%20corner%20furniture%20with%20a%20single%20sofa%20chair%20or%20a%20side%20table\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014048\/living-room-corner-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"Living room corner furniture with a single sofa chair or a side table\" class=\"wp-image-7145\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014048\/living-room-corner-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014048\/living-room-corner-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014048\/living-room-corner-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21014048\/living-room-corner-furniture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Use every opportunity to embellish your living room with furniture<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-furniture-design-ideas\/\">Living Room Furniture Design Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-wall-decor-ideas\/\">10 Brilliant Living Room Wall Decor Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Dreamy Interiors That Spell 'WOW'<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our design experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n   